import { HeaderContainer, VolumeContainer } from "./volume.styles"
import SearchBox from "../../components/search-box/search-box.component"

const VolumePage = () => {
	return (
		<VolumeContainer>
			<Header/>
			<HeaderContainer>Transaction History</HeaderContainer>
			<SearchBox onChangeHandler={onSearchChange} placeholder={"Enter your address"}/>
			<TransferContainer>
				<TextContainer bold>Daily volume</TextContainer>
				<TextContainer bold>Weekly volume</TextContainer>
				<TextContainer bold>Monthly volume</TextContainer>
			</TransferContainer>
			{
				<TransferContainer>
					<TextContainer>1000 ETH</TextContainer>
					<TextContainer>1000 ETH</TextContainer>
					<TextContainer>10000 ETH</TextContainer>
				</TransferContainer>
			}
		</VolumeContainer>
		
	)
}

export default VolumePage
